data.description: OPEN SUNDAY SEPT 24, 2-4PM! Looking for peace and quiet? Look no further! Welcome to this wonderful Willard home on 10 acres! BRAND NEW roof! As you turn on to the farm road you will feel the tranquility. As you enter you will feel the natural light beam through the living room. Open concept living and dining area with wonderful brick fireplace with blowers. The kitchen features island with new electric range, wrap around counters with view to the wonderful back yard. HUGE covered and screened back porch, TRANQUIL back yard with large water garden with irrigation, pergola, paver patio and much more. Main bedroom also on first level with ensuite bath. Additional front bedroom on main level currently being used as an office. Half bath off of the kitchen with pantry and access to 2 car garage. Downstairs you will find brand new carpet, large second living space with another fireplace and french doors out to rear patio and wet bar. 2 additional bedrooms downstairs, one also with access to rear with french doors. Full bath, utility room, and laundry space. Newer HVAC system, water softener, and home water filtration. This home features 2x6 exterior walls, newer windows, oversized storage areas. This home has been wonderfully maintained over the years and is ready for its new owners, do not miss this opportunity!
